{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"ImageTrack.selected","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageTrack/selected","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebCodecs_API\">WebCodecs API</a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Interfaces</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioData\"><code>AudioData</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioDecoder\"><code>AudioDecoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioEncoder\"><code>AudioEncoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EncodedAudioChunk\"><code>EncodedAudioChunk</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EncodedVideoChunk\"><code>EncodedVideoChunk</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageDecoder\"><code>ImageDecoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageTrack\"><code>ImageTrack</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageTrackList\"><code>ImageTrackList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VideoDecoder\"><code>VideoDecoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VideoEncoder\"><code>VideoEncoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VideoColorSpace\"><code>VideoColorSpace</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VideoFrame\"><code>VideoFrame</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <strong><code>selected</code></strong> property of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageTrack\"><code>ImageTrack</code></a> interface returns <code>true</code> if the track is selected for decoding.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"Value","isH3":false,"content":"<p>A <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>boolean</code></a>, if <code>true</code> the track is selected for decoding.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","t